{
  "stem": "2833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, well-- that's what they figured, that if we look up to the airplane who is God knows how high he will see us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were scared, they were shaking, they were grabbing our hands as long as they were outside with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The moment they were inside that had stopped, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But we loved it when we saw the planes coming, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one day we heard shooting far off, but still you could hear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And within a couple of days it got closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And one day, I-- oh, I forgot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was so weak and I felt so bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I had, in Theresien, had encephalitis and knew how, how it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I just told my girlfriend who was working with me, don't get scared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm just going to drop, and they have to take me to the-- back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there was one room where you could put somebody who was ill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they put me in there and there was one other girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we knew when there was three who are sick, they send you back to-- from there to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So we always, you know, tried to God forbid, not be three.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I pretended-- and the doctor, who was one of our prisoners who knew exactly what I'm doing, came with this SS doctor because he wanted to see what it's like if somebody has encephalitis.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I knew exactly how to react, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And so I stayed there a few days and really regained a little bit of strength.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then somebody else got hurt, so I got up and went back.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
